<lb n="0039b21"/><head type="no">No. 1209</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0039b22"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0039001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】延久六年寫高山寺藏本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，【丙】東寺三密藏古寫本，（降三世）＋金【甲】</note>金剛<note n="0039002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔頂〕－【甲】</note><app n="0039002"><lem>頂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>瑜伽<note n="0039003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔降三世〕－【甲】</note><app n="0039003"><lem>降三世</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>成就極深
<lb n="0039b23"/>密<note n="0039004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＋（法）【甲】</note><app n="0039004"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門法</rdg></app><note n="0039005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0039005"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0039b24"/>
<lb n="0039b25"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0039006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…空））四十三字＝（（唐特進試鴻臚卿大廣智不空三藏與淨行婆羅門遍智奉詔譯））二十五字【明】【乙】【丙】，（（遍智阿闍梨指授））七字【甲】</note><note n="0039006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（開府…空））四十三字＝（（唐特進試鴻臚卿大廣智不空三藏與淨行婆羅門遍智奉詔譯））二十五字【明】【乙】【丙】，＝（（遍智阿闍梨指授））七字【甲】</note><app n="0039006" word-count="43"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0039b26"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
