<lb n="0039b28"/>不空</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">唐特進試鴻臚卿大廣智不空三藏與淨行婆羅門遍智奉詔譯</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">遍智阿闍梨指授</rdg></app>奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0039b29"/><lg><l>歸命聖主宰</l><l>普賢金剛手</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1209.0039c" n="0039c"/>
<lb n="0039c01"/><l>為降伏一切</l><l>現吽迦<note n="0039007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0039007"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>身</l>
<lb n="0039c02"/><l><note n="0039008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摧＝推【明】</note><app n="0039008"><lem>摧</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">推</rdg></app>三世有毒</l><l>令即證菩提</l>
<lb n="0039c03"/><l>是甚深祕密</l><l>降三世瑜伽</l>
<lb n="0039c04"/><l>首依真實<note n="0039009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0039009"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app></l><l>禮淨<note n="0039010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＝令&M062403;【丙】</note><app n="0039010"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【丙】">令</rdg></app>縛摧</l>
<lb n="0039c05"/><l>入閉普賢印</l><l>按心稱本誓</l>
<lb n="0039c06"/><l>悅已又誦此</l></lg>
<lb n="0039c07"/><p type="dharani">摩<note n="0039011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝賀引【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0039011"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app>拘嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>馱薩怛<note n="0039012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝舞&M062403;【丙】</note><app n="0039012"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【丙】">舞</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0039013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合無保反＝無保切二合【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0039013"><lem>二合<note n="0039014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無保反〕－【甲】</note><app n="0039014"><lem>無保反</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">無保切二合</rdg></app></note><note n="0039015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唅＝憾【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0039015"><lem>唅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">憾</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0039c08"/><lg><l>發言身即同</l><l>降三世金剛</l>
<lb n="0039c09"/><l>四印加寶灌</l><l>鬘甲二擬繫</l>
<lb n="0039c10"/><l>拍掌同金剛</l><l>即入三摩地</l>
<lb n="0039c11"/><l>諦觀心阿字</l><l><note n="0039016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成＝或【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0039016"><lem>成</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">或</rdg></app>月或日輪</l>
<lb n="0039c12"/><l>中生五智杵</l><l>次請尊及佛</l>
<lb n="0039c13"/><l>入加三昧身</l><l>又以本教中</l>
<lb n="0039c14"/><l>四印加已滿</l><l>五寶鬘甲拍</l>
<lb n="0039c15"/><l>陳內外供養</l><l>讚詠<note n="0039017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【明】【乙】</note><app n="0039017"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>念誦</l>
<lb n="0039c16"/><l>若作圓具法</l><l>以五相成身</l>
<lb n="0039c17"/><l><note n="0039018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又＝及【明】【乙】</note><app n="0039018"><lem>又</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">及</rdg></app>普悅<note n="0039019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">本＝大【丙】</note><app n="0039019"><lem>本</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>誓</l><l>忿<note n="0039020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四印＝印四【甲】</note><app n="0039020"><lem>四印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">印四</rdg></app>五佛</l>
<lb n="0039c18"/><l>寶鬘甲拍等</l><l>以吽迦<note n="0039021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0039021"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>印</l>
<lb n="0039c19"/><l>加心誦真言</l></lg>
