<lb n="0040c04"/><p><note n="0040063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">步＝佛【明】</note><app n="0040063"><lem>步</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">佛</rdg></app>蹋時真言曰</p>
