<lb n="0040c06"/><lg><l>又見自心月</l><l>金剛具五&CB00123;</l>
<lb n="0040c07"/><l>中有所持明</l><l>流射金剛火</l>
<lb n="0040c08"/><l>住是<note n="0040069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝火【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040069"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">火</rdg></app>三昧</l><l>持根本真言</l>
<lb n="0040c09"/><l>或心一字明</l><l>或<note n="0040070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">業＝樂【明】【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040070"><lem>業</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">樂</rdg></app>心中心</l>
<lb n="0040c10"/><l>擿枳王真言</l><l>住定疲極已</l>
<lb n="0040c11"/><l>方坐誦讚歎</l><l>陳供及發願</l>
<lb n="0040c12"/><l>即<note n="0040071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＝是【明】</note><app n="0040071"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>解脫法</l><l>以本法四印</l>
<lb n="0040c13"/><l>四處掣開之</l></lg>
<lb n="0040c14"/><p>心上真言曰</p>
<lb n="0040c15"/><p type="dharani">唵<app type="＊" source="0040064"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>薩怛<app type="＊" source="0040065"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><app type="＊" source="0040065"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0040072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惹＝若【明】，入【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0040072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惹＝若【明】，＝入【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040072"><lem>惹</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">入</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0040065"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二<app type="＊" source="0039025"><lem>合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">合引</rdg></app></note>
